---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.vue';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Crews from '../components/Crews.astro';
import OurBlog from '../components/OurBlog.astro';
// import AboutUs_ from '../components/AboutUs.astro';

import banner from '../images/banner-2.jpg';

const currentPath = Astro.url.pathname;
---

<Layout title="PT. Azaku Nusantara Green">
	<Navbar client:only path={currentPath}/>
    <div class="lg:h-screen flex lg:flex-row flex-col mb-10 lg:mb-0">
        <div class="w-5/6 mx-auto lg:w-full lg:px-32 px-0">
            <h5 class="text-5xl font-extrabold pt-10 pb-10 md:text-left text-center">About Us</h5>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 text-lg">
                <p>In the heart of the lush Indonesian archipelago, Azaku Nusantara Green was born from a deep-rooted passion for agriculture and a commitment to cultivating sustainable, high-quality produce. Our journey began several decades ago when our founder, Haznam Amirullah, a visionary farmer, embarked on a mission to transform traditional farming practices into a thriving, eco-conscious agricultural enterprise.</p>
                <p>We started as a modest family farm, where every crop was nurtured with care, much like tending to one's own children. The land provided not only sustenance but also inspiration. It was amidst the vibrant green fields and pristine landscapes that the vision for Azaku Nusantara Green was conceived.</p>
                <p>Over the years, our dedication to innovation and the environment propelled us forward. We adopted cutting-edge farming techniques and embraced sustainable practices. Our commitment to using only the finest quality fertilizers and environmentally friendly methods became the hallmark of our success. This devotion to excellence led to the production of exceptional crops renowned for their taste, nutrition, and eco-friendliness.</p>
            </div> 
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden w-full h-72 lg:h-full hidden lg:block">
            <img src={banner.src} alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
    </div>
	<Crews />
    <div class="h-px bg-[#999] w-full mt-10"></div>
    <OurBlog header="Recent Updates"/>
	<Footer />
</Layout>

